title: Local Fraternity Shaves Heads to Support Breast Cancer Research (Columbus State University)
text: ( Source : Columbus State University ) COLUMBUS , Ga. - Columbus State University's Xi Iota Chapter of Kappa Sigma is raising money for breast cancer research by shaving the heads of their brothers during the annual 'Shave to Save ' event
